Accedence Long accidence. Stanbridge, John, 1463-1510, attributed name. Donatus, Aelius, attributed name.
[28] p.
In Caxtons hous by wynkyn de worde, [Prynted at westmynstre : [1499]]
Sometimes attributed to John Stanbridge and to Aelius Donatus. Place of publication and printer's name from colophon; publication date conjectured by STC. Signatures: A B⁴. Formerly STC 7010. Identified as STC 7010 on UMI microfilm reel 61. Reproduction of the original in the Bodleian Library.
